definition.value: A linear amino tetrasaccharide consisting of alpha-D-galactose, beta-D-galactose, N-acetyl-beta-D-glucosamine and (at the reducing end) N-acetyl-alpha-D-galactosamine residues linked conesecutively (1->3), (1->4) and (1->3).
A D-mannofuranose that has beta configuration at the anomeric centre.
